      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk im just really worried cause i also feel kinda hot and my mouth is super dry. i usually take insulin when i feel like my levels are high to get them under control... i feel like if i just take a small corrective dose of maybe 2 units it'll balance everything out? won't that help more than just eating sugar?",
